             int userID,
             java.lang.String eventName,
             java.lang.String description,
             java.lang.String start,
             java.lang.String end,
             java.lang.String location,
             java.lang.String occurrence)
        Create an event will all the details provided
        Parameters:
        eventName - Name of the event
        description - details about the event
        start - the start time of event
        end - end time of the event in string format
        location - the location of the event in string format
        occurrence - how often the event occurs. legal arguments: ONCE, EVERYDAY, WEEK, MONTH, YEAR. By default it is ONCE.
        id - The id of the event
        userID - The id of the user that created the event
